ies mwx-AhMkwr qoN (BweIcwrk jIvn ivc) keI ivgwV c`l pYNdy hn ]1] rhwau]
hryk mnu`K iehI AwKdw hY ik (bRwhmx, K`qRI, vYS, SUdr, ieh) cwr hI (vK vK) vrn hn[
(pr ieh lok ieh nhIN smJdy ik) prmwqmw dI joiq-rUp Asly qoN hI swrI isRStI pYdw huMdI hY ]2]
ieh swrw sMswr hY (prmwqmw ny AwpxI hI joiq qoN bxwieAw hoieAw hY),
(ijvyN koeI) GuimAwr ieko im`tI qoN keI iksmW dy BWfy GV lYNdw hY ]3]
pMj q`q iml ky srIr dI Skl bxdI hY[
koeI ieh nhIN AwK skdw ik iksy (vrn vwly) ivc bhuqy q`q hn, qy, iksy (vrn vwly) ivc QoVHy q`q hn ]4]
nwnk AwKdw hY ik (BwvyN koeI bRwhmx hY, BwvyN koeI SUdr hY) hryk jIv Awpo Awpxy kIqy krmW (dy sMskwrW) dw b`Jw hoieAw hY[
gurU nUM imlx qoN ibnw (kIqy krmW dy sMskwrW dy bMDnW qoN) ^lwsI nhIN huMdI ]5]1]
