jogI, igRhsqI, pMifq, ByKW dy swDU-
ieh swry Awpo Awpxy (iksy) AhMkwr ivc (pY ky pRBU dI Xwd vloN) Zw&il hoey rihMdy hn ]1]
jIv mwieAw dy (moh dy) nSy ivc msq ho ky pRBU dI Xwd vloN Zw&il hoieAw rihMdw hY (qy, ies dy Awqmk jIvn dI rws-pUMjI nUM kwmwidk lu`tdy rihMdy hn)[
pr ijhVw mnu`K (pRBU dI Xwd dI brkiq nwl) sucyq rihMdw hY, aus nUM koeI ivkwr lu`t nhIN skdw ]1] rhwau]
isr& auh mnu`K sucyq rihMdw hY ijs nUM gurU iml pYNdw hY[
auh mnu`K (ismrn dI brkiq nwl) kwmwidk pMjy vYrIAW nUM Awpxy v`s ivc krI r`Kdw hY ]2]
auh mnu`K (ivkwrW vloN) Awpxy Awp nUM bcweI r`Kdw hY, auh mnu`K hornW auqy D`kw-vDIkI nhIN krdw
jo prmwqmw dy guxW nUM Awpxy mn ivc vsWdw hY[ isr& auh mnu`K sucyq rihMdw hY ]3]
isr& auh mnu`K (mwieAw dy moh dI nINd vloN) sucyq rihMdw hY ijhVw isr& prmwqmw nwl fUMGI sWJ pWdw hY,
ijhVw mwieAw (dy moh) nUM iqAwgdw hY, Aqy Awpxy Asly-pRBU nwl jwx-pCwx bxWdw hY ]4]
(koeI bRwhmx hovy K`qRI hovy vYS hovy SUdr hovy) cOhW vrnW ivcoN koeI ivrlw (mwieAw dy moh dI nINd qoN) sucyq rihMdw hY (iksy ^ws vrn dw koeI ilhwz nhIN)[
(ijhVw jwgdw hY, auh) Awqmk mOq qoN bicAw rihMdw hY ]5]
nwnk AwKdw hY ik auh mnu`K mwieAw dy moh dI nINd qoN jwgdw hY,
ijs dIAW A`KW ivc Awqmk jIvn dI sUJ dw surmw ipAw huMdw hY ]6]2]
