Asl mon-DwrI swDU auh hY ijhVw (Awpxy) mn dI myr-qyr mukw dyNdw hY,
Aqy myr-qyr mukw ky (aus myr-qyr dy QW) prmwqmw nUM (Awpxy) mn ivc vsWdw hY ]1]
hy BweI! Awpxy ies mn nUM Kojdy irhw kro[
mn (dI dOV-B`j) dI pVqwl kridAW prmwqmw dw nwm iml jWdw hY, ies nwm hI (mwno) DrqI dy swry nO ^zwny hY ]1] rhwau]
(jgq-rcnw dy) mu`F moh nUM bxw ky krqwr ny jgq pYdw kIqw[
jIvW nUM Apx`q cMboV ky (mwieAw dI ^wqr) Btkxw ivc pw ky (aus ny Awp hI) kurwhy pw id`qw ]2]
ieh mn (dy myr-qyr Apx`q Awidk dy sMskwrW) qoN hI swrw jnm mrn dw islislw bxdw hY[
mn dy (suc`jy) vIcwr dI rwhIN prmwqmw dI rzw nUM smJ ky jIv prmwqmw ivc lIn ho jWdw hY ]3]
